#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.162"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.162:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.162:0.2"
msgid "17. Paṭipadāvagga"
msgstr "17. Practice"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: dutiyapaṭipadāsuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.162:0.3"
msgid "162. Vitthārasutta"
msgstr "162. In Detail"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.162:1.1"
msgid "“Catasso imā, bhikkhave, paṭipadā."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are four ways of practice."

msgctxt "an4.162:1.2"
msgid "Katamā catasso?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.162:1.3"
msgid ""
"Dukkhā paṭipadā dandhābhiññā, dukkhā paṭipadā khippābhiññā, sukhā paṭipadā "
"dandhābhiññā, sukhā paṭipadā khippābhiññā."
msgstr ""
"~Painful practice with slow insight, ~painful practice with swift insight, ~"
"pleasant practice with slow insight, and ~pleasant practice with swift "
"insight."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.162:2.1"
msgid "Katamā ca, bhikkhave, dukkhā paṭipadā dandhābhiññā?"
msgstr "And what’s the painful practice with slow insight?"

msgctxt "an4.162:2.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco pakatiyāpi tibbarāgajātiko hoti, abhikkhaṇaṃ rāgajaṃ "
"dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti."
msgstr ""
"It’s when someone is ordinarily full of acute greed, hate, and delusion. "
"They often feel the pain and sadness that greed, hate, and delusion bring."

msgctxt "an4.162:2.3"
msgid ""
"Pakatiyāpi tibbadosajātiko hoti, abhikkhaṇaṃ dosajaṃ dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ "
"paṭisaṃvedeti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.162:2.4"
msgid ""
"Pakatiyāpi tibbamohajātiko hoti, abhikkhaṇaṃ mohajaṃ dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ "
"paṭisaṃvedeti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.162:2.5"
msgid "Tassimāni pañcindriyāni mudūni pātubhavanti—"
msgstr "They have these five faculties weakly:"

msgctxt "an4.162:2.6"
msgid ""
"saddhindriyaṃ, vīriyindriyaṃ, satindriyaṃ, samādhindriyaṃ, paññindriyaṃ."
msgstr "faith, energy, mindfulness, immersion, and wisdom."

msgctxt "an4.162:2.7"
msgid ""
"So imesaṃ pañcannaṃ indriyānaṃ muduttā dandhaṃ ānantariyaṃ pāpuṇāti āsavānaṃ "
"khayāya."
msgstr ""
"Because of this, they only slowly attain the conditions for ending the "
"defilements in the present life."

msgctxt "an4.162:2.8"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, dukkhā paṭipadā dandhābhiññā."
msgstr "This is called the painful practice with slow insight."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.150"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.162:3.1"
msgid "Katamā ca, bhikkhave, dukkhā paṭipadā khippābhiññā?"
msgstr "And what’s the painful practice with swift insight?"

msgctxt "an4.162:3.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco pakatiyāpi tibbarāgajātiko hoti, abhikkhaṇaṃ rāgajaṃ "
"dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti."
msgstr ""
"It’s when someone is ordinarily full of acute greed, hate, and delusion. "
"They often feel the pain and sadness that greed, hate, and delusion bring."

msgctxt "an4.162:3.3"
msgid ""
"Pakatiyāpi tibbadosajātiko hoti, abhikkhaṇaṃ dosajaṃ dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ "
"paṭisaṃvedeti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.162:3.4"
msgid ""
"Pakatiyāpi tibbamohajātiko hoti, abhikkhaṇaṃ mohajaṃ dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ "
"paṭisaṃvedeti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.162:3.5"
msgid "Tassimāni pañcindriyāni adhimattāni pātubhavanti—"
msgstr "And they have these five faculties strongly:"

msgctxt "an4.162:3.6"
msgid ""
