msgctxt "an4.162:3.8"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, dukkhā paṭipadā khippābhiññā."
msgstr "This is called the painful practice with swift insight."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an4.162:4.1"
msgid "Katamā ca, bhikkhave, sukhā paṭipadā dandhābhiññā?"
msgstr "And what’s pleasant practice with slow insight?"

msgctxt "an4.162:4.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco pakatiyāpi na tibbarāgajātiko hoti, nābhikkhaṇaṃ "
"rāgajaṃ dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti."
msgstr ""
"It’s when someone is not ordinarily full of acute greed, hate, and delusion. "
"They rarely feel the pain and sadness that greed, hate, and delusion bring."

msgctxt "an4.162:4.3"
msgid ""
"Pakatiyāpi na tibbadosajātiko hoti, nābhikkhaṇaṃ dosajaṃ dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ "
"paṭisaṃvedeti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.162:4.4"
msgid ""
"Pakatiyāpi na tibbamohajātiko hoti, nābhikkhaṇaṃ mohajaṃ dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ "
"paṭisaṃvedeti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.162:4.5"
msgid "Tassimāni pañcindriyāni mudūni pātubhavanti—"
msgstr "They have these five faculties weakly:"

msgctxt "an4.162:4.6"
msgid "saddhindriyaṃ … pe … paññindriyaṃ."
msgstr "faith, energy, mindfulness, immersion, and wisdom."

msgctxt "an4.162:4.7"
msgid ""
"So imesaṃ pañcannaṃ indriyānaṃ muduttā dandhaṃ ānantariyaṃ pāpuṇāti āsavānaṃ "
"khayāya."
msgstr ""
"Because of this, they only slowly attain the conditions for ending the "
"defilements in the present life."

msgctxt "an4.162:4.8"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, sukhā paṭipadā dandhābhiññā."
msgstr "This is called the pleasant practice with slow insight."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
